<div id="readme">
<h2>The Collector</h2>
<ul>

<li><strong>High Concept:</strong>
Collect artifacts while changing size.
</li>

<li><strong>Player Experience Goals:</strong>
Platforming with a little big twist.
</li>

<li><strong>Genre:</strong>
Platformer.
</li>

<li><strong>Game play:</strong>
Use the left and right arrow keys to move, up to grow, down to shrink, and space to jump.
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype goal:</strong>
Make a platformer with item collection and shrink/grow mechanics.
</li>

<li><strong>Features:</strong>
Platforming with a shrink/grow mechanic.
</li>

<li><strong>Setting/Premise:</strong>
You have been subject to a medical experiment allowing you to shrink and grow at will to a predetermined size. You must collect round artifacts scattered throughout the map.
</li>

<li><strong>Story:</strong>
None.
</li>

<li><strong>Target Audience:</strong>
Everyone 10 and up who has interest in platformers, collecting stuff, shrinking, and growing.
</li>

<li><strong>Play time:</strong>
1-5 mins.
</li>

<li><strong>Strategies:</strong>
Shrink and grow when you need to, and don't forget your jump height is also affected.
</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Assets:</strong>
Tilemap: Buch http://opengameart.org/content/the-field-of-the-floating-islands 
Sprites by Antifarea: 
http://opengameart.org/content/antifareas-rpg-sprite-set-1-enlarged-w-transparent-background-fixed 
Beep: 
https://www.freesound.org/people/pan14/sounds/263133/ 
Select: 
https://www.freesound.org/people/killkhan/sounds/150222/ 
Jump: 
http://opengameart.org/content/jump-sound-effect-yo-frankie 
Music: 
"Late Night Sneakin" (HappyBivouac / http://ocremix.org) 

</li>

<li><strong>Prototype Closest Other Game:</strong>

</li>

</ul>
